{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Contact the Driving Standards Agency (DSA)"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/contact-driving-standards-agency-dsa.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/contact-driving-standards-agency-dsa"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"2395","business_proposition":false,"alternative_title":"","overview":"Contact the Driving Standards Agency (DSA) - email, phone, letter, driving test, practical driving test","updated_at":"2012-10-09T18:13:59+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>There are different contact details for the Driving Standards Agency (<abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>) depending on your enquiry.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Check the <a href=\"/browse/driving\" title=\"Driving section\">driving section</a> first to see if your question is answered there.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Theory tests</h2>\n\n<p>You can use the following ways to contact the <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> about theory tests.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> theory test bookings and enquiries</strong></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#099;&#117;&#115;&#116;&#111;&#109;&#101;&#114;&#099;&#097;&#114;&#101;&#064;&#112;&#101;&#097;&#114;&#115;&#111;&#110;&#046;&#099;&#111;&#109;\">&#099;&#117;&#115;&#116;&#111;&#109;&#101;&#114;&#099;&#097;&#114;&#101;&#064;&#112;&#101;&#097;&#114;&#115;&#111;&#110;&#046;&#099;&#111;&#109;</a><br />\n<strong>Telephone:</strong> 0300 200 1122 (English bookings), 0300 200 1188 (English enquiries) 0300 200 1133 (Welsh bookings)<br />\n<strong>Textphone:</strong> 0300 200 1166<br />\n<strong>Fax:</strong> 0300 200 1177<br />\nMonday to Friday 8am to 4pm</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\n\n<br /><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>\n<br />PO BOX 381\n<br />M50 3UW \n<br />\n<br />\n</p></div></div>\n\n<h2>Practical tests</h2>\n\n<p>You can use the following information or the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://forms.direct.gov.uk/forms/form/273/en\" title=\"Contact the DSA\">use the online service</a> to contact the <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> about practical tests.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> practical test bookings and enquiries</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Telephone:</strong> 0300 200 1122 (English), 0300 200 1133 (Welsh)<br />\n<strong>Textphone:</strong> 0300 200 1144<br />\n<strong>Fax:</strong> 0300 200 1155<br />\nMonday to Friday 8am to 4pm</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\n\n<br /><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>\n<br />PO Box 280\n<br />Newcastle-Upon-Tyne\n<br />NE99 1FP \n<br />\n<br />\n</p></div></div>\n\n<h2>General enquiries</h2>\n\n<p>You can use the following information to contact the <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> with a general enquiry.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> customer service centre</strong></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#099;&#117;&#115;&#116;&#111;&#109;&#101;&#114;&#046;&#115;&#101;&#114;&#118;&#105;&#099;&#101;&#115;&#064;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#046;&#103;&#115;&#105;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#099;&#117;&#115;&#116;&#111;&#109;&#101;&#114;&#046;&#115;&#101;&#114;&#118;&#105;&#099;&#101;&#115;&#064;&#100;&#115;&#097;&#046;&#103;&#115;&#105;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n<strong>Telephone:</strong> 0300 200 1122 (English), 0300 200 1133 (Welsh)<br />\n<strong>Textphone:</strong> 0300 200 1144<br />\n<strong>Fax:</strong> 0300 200 1155<br />\nMonday to Friday 8am to 4pm</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\n\n<br /><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>\n<br />PO Box 280\n<br />Newcastle-Upon-Tyne\n<br />NE99 1FP \n<br />\n<br />\n</p></div></div>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Driving tests and learning to drive","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/driving%2Flearning-to-drive.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes booking a test, changing and cancelling tests, rules and fees","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=driving%2Flearning-to-drive","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving/learning-to-drive"},"parent":{"title":"Driving","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/driving.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Book your driving test or get a tax disc online, find out the legal requirements for buying, owning, importing or scrapping a car or motorcycle, and read about your rights and responsibilities as a driver.","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=driving","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving"},"parent":null}}]],["related",[{"title":"Book your practical driving test","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/book-practical-driving-test.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/book-practical-driving-test","format":"transaction","details":{"need_id":"858","business_proposition":false}},{"title":"Book your driving theory test","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/book-a-driving-theory-test.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/book-a-driving-theory-test","format":"transaction","details":{"need_id":"859","business_proposition":false}},{"title":"Change the date of your practical driving test","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/change-date-practical-driving-test.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/change-date-practical-driving-test","format":"transaction","details":{"need_id":"1892","business_proposition":false}},{"title":"Driving test costs","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.u